INSERT INTO databasenode VALUES(7146,'2021-09-24T23:18:55','2021-09-24T22:18:55',NULL,'2021-09-26T15:00:31','2021-09-26T14:00:31','logitech-streamcam-camera-not-available-at-1080-60fps-full-hd-solution','publish','post','https://raddy.co.uk/blog/logitech-streamcam-camera-not-available-at-1080-60fps-full-hd-solution/',NULL,'
<p>I bought my Logitech Streamcam new from Amazon and directly used the Type C Port without any adapters. Unfortunately, I was unable to have the Full HD (1080p 60fps) working. It would only work sometimes when I restart my PC and then usually displays &#8220;Camera not available&#8221;. By the way, I am on Windows 10 with NVIDIA GeForce GTX 970.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="552" src="https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads//2021/09/camera-not-available-1024x552.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-7149" srcset="https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/camera-not-available-1024x552.jpg 1024w, https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/camera-not-available-300x162.jpg 300w, https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/camera-not-available-768x414.jpg 768w, https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/camera-not-available-1536x828.jpg 1536w, https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/camera-not-available.jpg 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>The <a href="https://support.logi.com/hc/en-us/articles/360043221373-Getting-Started-Logitech-StreamCam" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Logitech Streamcam &#8220;Getting Started&#8221;</a> guide shows that Type C ports and USB 3.0 should work. Unfortunately for me, the Type C port didn&#8217;t work and I had to purchase a converter.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" width="500" height="226" src="https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads//2021/09/QSG_3.jpg" alt="StreamCam Connectivity" class="wp-image-7148" srcset="https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/QSG_3.jpg 500w, https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/QSG_3-300x136.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></figure></div>



<p>An interesting thing happened as I was debugging the issue. For some reason, the thruput is too much on my USB Type C port.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" width="448" height="266" src="https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads//2021/09/controller-resources-exceeded.jpg" alt="controller-resources-exceeded" class="wp-image-7147" srcset="https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/controller-resources-exceeded.jpg 448w, https://g8b9j5b9.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/controller-resources-exceeded-300x178.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px" /></figure></div>



<h2>Solution</h2>



<p>Try using a regular 3.0 USB port with a USB converter. You need to search for &#8220;<strong>USB C Female to USB Male Adapter 3.1 or 3.0</strong>&#8220;.</p>



<p>Here are two affiliate links to Amazon products that should work. You might as well invest in a USB 3.1 adaptor as the price is almost the same as USB 3.0. I went for the first smaller and cheaper convertor. </p>



<a href="https://www.amazon.co.uk/OMOTON-Adapter-Converter-Compatible-Chargers/dp/B08XTSFTLM?dchild=1&amp;keywords=USB+C+Female+to+USB+Male+Adapter+3.1&amp;qid=1632521004&amp;qsid=260-9403885-1563533&amp;sr=8-5&amp;sres=B07MRCZTD1%2CB087R1GZ1Q%2CB08XTSFTLM%2CB07LFMWSCY%2CB078HRTQG7%2CB094HXC4VB%2CB085VT1VJT%2CB09BJP78PW%2CB077FY7831%2CB075B1T4Y9%2CB079K773M7%2CB088FJSD4B%2CB07Z662186%2CB083DS8GDH%2CB07TJ38SDW%2CB07XRF3KRP&amp;srpt=ELECTRONIC_ADAPTER&amp;linkCode=li2&amp;tag=raddythebra05-21&amp;linkId=9410e4f91c68f46302a5c570641c3164&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img border="0" src="//ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B08XTSFTLM&amp;Format=_SL160_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=raddythebra05-21&amp;language=en_GB"></a><img loading="lazy" src="https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=raddythebra05-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li2&amp;o=2&amp;a=B08XTSFTLM" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;">



