  }
}</pre></div>



<p>Note that the version of the dependencies might change in the future.</p>



<h2>3) Project Structure</h2>



<p>Our project is going to be simple. </p>



<pre class="wp-block-preformatted"> node_modules
 views
  pages
   index.ejs
 app.js - create this file
